(348, 'Pokus AI — Investor deck summary: - Problem - Urban consumers spend significant time on operational chores and recurring tasks. These involve research, coordination, booking, negotiation, and follow‑ups. - Solution - A WhatsApp-first “personal assistant in your pocket” that combines AI automation with human ops for edge cases and physical execution. - Aim: move from reactive task handling to proactive, workflow-led assistance via a memory layer and recommendations - Product and workflows - Handles ad‑hoc and recurring tasks: home repairs, vendor coordination, cab bookings, refunds, gifting, licenses, etc. - Examples of automated or semi‑automated workflows: weekly groceries, daily porter, routine cab bookings, medicine reminders/refills, restaurant reservations, gifting cadences. - Approach and tech - Hybrid Human + AI architecture. - Modular stack: AI Relationship Manager for memory and recommendations, Executor OS for task capture, grading, SOP generation, and a copilot for human operators. - Progressive automation roadmap across planning, search, subjective research, booking, calling, form filling, coordination, summarization. - ICP and use cases - 25–28: lifestyle and exploratory tasks. - 28–35: self and parents use cases, home management becomes sticky. - 35+: higher value “function outsourcing” such as home manager, recurring logistics, and family routines. - Positioning gravitates toward a “household COO” for families and busy professionals.[ - Traction - ~60 paying su...'),
(349, 'Company Overview & Founder Profile (Feb 2026) - 2026-02-27: AI-powered fashion discovery platform — personalized outfit recommendations, virtual try-ons, and style inspiration. Swipe-based UI for outfit curation, brand filtering, budget-aware suggestions. Founded Jun 2024, bootstrapped. FOUNDER: • Shekhar Chatterjee — Co-founder/CEO. Ashoka University (CS + Entrepreneurship, PG Diploma). Serial founder: SmartCitizen Labs (emergency response app, won UN Karmaveer Chakra), NoCap Meta (VR solution, raised ₹2cr per The Hindu), NoCap Research (managed ₹1.2cr AUM, 45% returns over 28mo). Also: Head of Engineering at Neuroute (clinical dev platform, London), Consultant at EXL, NVIDIA intern, Director of Technology at Harvard US-India Initiative. Based in Vadodara. LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/shekharchatterjee/ ATTIO CRM: • Email activity: Feb 26, 2026 • Meeting: Feb 27, 2026 • Domain: polopan.com Link to the MIS - [https://polopan.com/analytics.html](https://polopan.com/analytics.html) SOURCE: Trinika flagged in Consumer + DeVC group (Feb 27, 2026) --- **TK Views ** - **TK View: WM ** - Spikey: 0 - Spikey Needed: Consumer, and product - ++ High IQ and first principled - ++ Understand P&L – comes from exporter family in Gujrat - ++ Numerate and analytical ++ Outside in – aware of shoppin failure points and in touch with shlok - ++ customer backward thinking - ++ Great techie - ?? difficult market to win – thin stack + low AOV because T2/3 - ?? Have been dabbling around with...'),
